note over browser
user writes "New note"
and hits the submit button
end note

note over browser
browser adds "New note"
to its local list of notes
and re-renders the list
on the page
end note

note over browser
browser sends "New note"
to the server
end note

browser->server: HTTP POST https://studies.cs.helsinki.fi/exampleapp/new_note_spa
server-->browser: {"message":"note created"}
